# Local-extraction training/eval ARTIFACTS — never source control:
#  • models/ root holds 13GB of weights/run outputs (qwen_resolver_mlx etc.)
#  • data/ + data_eval/ are training/eval jsonl DERIVED FROM the user's
#    personal documents — committing would publish library excerpts
#  • fixtures hold verbatim book chunks (same leak concern)
# Anchored to repo root: backend/models/ is Python source (Pydantic schemas),
# NOT weights, and must stay tracked.
/models/
data/
data_eval/
scripts/local_extraction_fixtures/
